{"word":"ὑποκινέω","slug":"ὑποκινέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποκινέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to move lightly</i>, <el>Ζεφύρου ὑποκινήσαντος</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>τὸ κῠμα</el>) <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to urge gently on</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to move a little, stir a finger</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to be deranged</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}